---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Hello World"
  description="An introduction to why I started this blog and what I plan to write about."
>
  <article class="page-content">

    <header class="post-header">
      <div class="post-meta">
        <span>May 10, 2026</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>2 min read</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Hello World</h1>
      <p class="post-lead">
        A quick note on why I'm starting this blog and what I plan to use it for.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="post-body">
      <p>
        I've been meaning to start writing for a while now. Not as a polished publication —
        more as a place to think out loud. Software development moves fast, and I find that
        writing things down is one of the best ways to actually consolidate what I'm learning.
      </p>
      <p>
        So that's what this blog is going to be. A running set of notes on things I'm working
        through, tools I'm experimenting with, patterns I've found useful, and the occasional
        opinion on where I think things are heading. Nothing exhaustive — just honest,
        first-hand takes from someone who spends most of their day writing .NET and thinking
        about distributed systems.
      </p>
      <p>
        Right now I'm particularly interested in how teams are integrating AI tooling into
        their day-to-day development workflows, how .NET Aspire is shaping the way we build
        and run cloud-native applications, and the ongoing shift toward event-driven
        architectures in enterprise software. Those topics will likely show up here a fair
        bit to start.
      </p>
      <p>
        If any of that sounds interesting, stick around. More posts to follow.
      </p>
    </div>

    <footer class="post-footer">
      <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-secondary">← Back to Blog</a>
    </footer>

  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style lang="scss">
@use '../../styles/styles' as *;

.page-content {
  padding-top: 3rem;
}

.post-header {
  padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid $surface;
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
}

.post-meta {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  color: $text-subtle;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

h1 {
  font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin: 0 0 1rem;
  color: $heading;
}

.post-lead {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
  color: $text-muted;
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 640px;
}

.post-body {
  h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    color: $heading;
  }

  p {
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
    color: $text-muted;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    max-width: 680px;
  }
}

.post-footer {
  padding-top: 3rem;
  border-top: 1px solid $surface;
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
</style>
